{"tid":655983,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同條女去澳門旅遊 撞到女友以前班舊同學..","createTime":"2018-05-07T00:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T06:17:50.000Z","uid":31323,"like":11,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e89dff79f6c526551edb86d0f8ba5a464b521d02","tid":655983,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:11:42.000Z","msg":"女友其實一早已經叫我陪佢去澳門玩 因為佢老豆做生意既關係 佢中學初中果陣係澳門讀過幾年書 <br />\n<br />\n一直都話好掛住澳門 想番去睇睇 但我推左2年都唔肯陪佢番去 原因當然係錢啦 嘩大佬 <br />\n<br />\n去澳門又遠又貴 你以為係澳洲咩 話去就想即刻去 當然唔得啦 但上星期因為我有D小事激嬲左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以冇辦法 比佢拉左去澳門玩 今日到達澳門第1日 我已經感覺到好唔舒服 因為周街都係大陸人 <br />\n<br />\n唔係因為大陸人生得柒 著衫柒 成個人成身都柒 係因為佢地有錢 大家都知我份人好仇富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n話咁快 我地就到左一個唔知咩門 後面成個大門咁 好多人係到影相又剩 都唔撚明有乜好影 <br />\n<br />\n忽然間後面有人大叫:喂 係咪你啊 MARY 我心諗:咦 去到喱到都有人識我條女 唔係掛 <br />\n<br />\n我條女一另轉面 佢就同果2個女仔FD攬一攬 原來係以前既初中同學 <br />\n<br />\n喱個時候我就想扮唔識我女友 因為果2條囡囡好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想溝佢地 <br />\n<br />\n佢朋友問:咦 你男朋友啊? 咁矮既?哈哈 <br />\n<br />\n我心諗:屌你把口洗唔洗咁臭啊 我假假地都167 咁都叫矮 你條8婆都係162左右炸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n之後我女友就想幫我解圍 佢話:介紹比你識啊 我中學同學 MAY同JUNE啊 <br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後就呆左呆 乜原來有人用月份黎改英文名架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我忍住笑 想曲線串果2條8婆 我話:你好你好 我叫DECEMBER啊 <br />\n<br />\n佢地一聽到 就係到爆笑 話:乜有人用月份黎改英文名架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我話:係囉係囉 原來真係有架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喱個時候 我女友係旁邊大力踢左我一野話:咪玩野啦頂你 <br />\n<br />\n我就即刻狗縮 企係我女友後面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉 希望唔會再撞到佢地朋友 而家番酒店先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa41659d9632f4c68b195e961cbefb5eefbc75d","tid":655983,"uid":56878,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},{"pid":"0df3d54e5d7f684aa95d5b39bee0da5521a8e5ae","tid":655983,"uid":59908,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:14:00.000Z","msg":"重點係篇嘢紅字到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a1e2a77af124036991cdb9c4cd521ad22b8a26","tid":655983,"uid":14413,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:14:15.000Z","msg":"都唔知你up嘜<br />\n又1999又唔好笑"},{"pid":"ca127ca2dca947f60879f43e11988d7e34e8f649","tid":655983,"uid":10079,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:16:05.000Z","msg":"紅字為笑點"},{"pid":"eb17e9603a2f08504326bd35f66c6d652316a404","tid":655983,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:26:34.000Z","msg":"點解我會笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8610826e4bc81f326b903ab74d9d249cfc7048","tid":655983,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:28:48.000Z","msg":"廢閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adf81081395fd95959db5f582594db7a60f14b4","tid":655983,"uid":3